// ---- Back Stack flows ----

// 1. Normal navigation:
Home → A → B → C → D
Back: D → C → B → A → Home

// 2. Navigate with popUpTo:
Home → A → B
popUpTo(Home) → Home (clears A, B)

// 3. popUpTo inclusive:
Home → A → B
popUpTo(Home, inclusive = true) → Home (clears everything)

// 4. Login flow:
Home → Login → (Login Success) → Home (stack cleared)

// 5. Back to Home from deep:
Home → A → B → C → D
Back to Home → Home (clears A, B, C, D)

